videos.title: Fynn is So Toxic  $90 Budget Magic
videos.description:
Fynn, the Fangbearer is back in Standard. Last time, it had literally zero support. Does the toxic mechanic mean Fynn might be good this time around? Let's find out!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
